title: Superman 001 (1939) (Digital) (TLK-EMPIRE-HD)
description:
Superman 001 (1939) (Digital) (TLK-EMPIRE-HD)

Yes, it's the first issue of Superman, presented in digital-HD thanks to Tyrant Lizard King-Empire. The plots are nonsense, the "action" is less than thrilling by today's standards, the villians are all boring crooks and Martha Kent is still known only as "Mary". BUT, it's still classic and worth a read if you are a fan of the Man of Steel. Thanks to the scanners for their efforts, please seed and enjoy! :-)
